---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About AymanCare — Dr. Ajaz Khan &amp; Our Team"
  description="Meet Dr. Ajaz Khan, MD and the AymanCare team. Compassionate primary and urgent care serving Dallas, North Richland Hills, Mesquite and Valley Ranch since 2013."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"About\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/about/\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>About</span>
  </div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <h1 class="page-title fade-in">Connecting you with<br>the <em>finest</em> care<br>in Dallas.</h1>
    <p class="about-tagline fade-in">"Our mission is to help you maintain a high quality of life through best health practices — and our entire staff is dedicated to this goal."</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="stats-band">
  <div class="stat-col fade-in">
    <div class="n">10<em>+</em></div>
    <div class="l">Years serving<br>DFW communities</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-col fade-in">
    <div class="n">04</div>
    <div class="l">Neighborhood<br>clinics</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-col fade-in">
    <div class="n"><em>ABFM</em></div>
    <div class="l">Board-certified<br>family medicine</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-col fade-in">
    <div class="n">4.8<em>★</em></div>
    <div class="l">Google rating<br>from 200+ patients</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="dr-khan">
  <div class="dr-khan-grid">
    <div class="dr-khan-img fade-in">
      <img src="/images/staff-photo.jpg" alt="Dr. Ajaz Khan, MD" loading="lazy">
      <div class="dr-khan-plate">
        <div class="l">✦ Medical Director</div>
        <div class="n">Ajaz Omer Khan, M.D.</div>
        <div class="c">American Board of Family Medicine</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="dr-khan-body">
      <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 24px; display: block;">◆ Meet Dr. Khan</span>
      <h2 class="fade-in">A whole-person<br>approach to <em>care.</em></h2>
      <blockquote class="fade-in">"The goal isn't to treat illness. It's to know the person well enough to help them stay healthy in the first place."</blockquote>
      <p class="fade-in">Dr. Ajaz Omer Khan is certified by the American Board of Family Medicine and continues to meet the requirements of his specialty medical board for ongoing learning and assessment — a commitment to lifelong growth and self-evaluation that keeps his practice at the leading edge.</p>
      <p class="fade-in">At AymanCare, we focus on your whole well-being, using data and technology to coordinate services and enhance care. But at its best, medicine is still deeply human — and that's the foundation we build every visit on.</p>
      <div class="dr-khan-chips fade-in">
        <span class="doctor-chip">ABFM Certified</span>
        <span class="doctor-chip accent">10+ years practicing</span>
        <span class="doctor-chip">All ages welcome</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="mission-section">
    <h2 class="fade-in">Our<br><em>clinic.</em></h2>
    <div>
      <p class="fade-in">At AymanCare Primary & Urgent Care, patients find what they need to protect and support their health — whether that's urgent care, pediatric care, or a partner to join them on their health journey. As a walk-in clinic and primary care provider, Dr. Khan and his team of experienced, qualified healthcare providers are dedicated to serving the communities of Dallas, Mesquite, North Richland Hills, and Valley Ranch.</p>
      <p class="fade-in">AymanCare blends primary care with services designed to support the health of entire families at a moment's notice. The team is seasoned at addressing medical emergencies like injuries and sudden illnesses. At the same time, their expertise in taking care of kids ensures that all pediatric patients feel comfortable and relaxed.</p>
      <p class="fade-in">Whether patients are looking for medical treatment for a pressing condition — like flu symptoms or strep throat — or are looking for a dedicated team of primary caregivers, AymanCare delivers. We offer a range of healthcare services designed to help patients lead their healthiest, most balanced lives, including weight loss programs, allergy testing, and treatment.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div>
      <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ What we stand for</span>
      <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Three principles shape<br>every <em>patient visit.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-subtitle fade-in">The way we practice medicine isn't about technology or trends. It's about three commitments we keep, every day.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="values-grid">
    <div class="value-card fade-in">
      <div class="value-num">01</div>
      <h3>Whole-person <em>care</em></h3>
      <p>We don't just treat symptoms. We use data and technology to coordinate services and see the whole picture — so every recommendation fits the person in front of us.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card fade-in">
      <div class="value-num">02</div>
      <h3>Accessible & <em>affordable</em></h3>
      <p>We accept all major insurance providers and are committed to easy, transparent billing. Walk-ins welcome. Same-day appointments available.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card fade-in">
      <div class="value-num">03</div>
      <h3>Lifelong <em>learning</em></h3>
      <p>Board certification is the start, not the end. Dr. Khan commits to ongoing assessment and continuous improvement — so your care reflects current best practice.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="team-feature-band">
  <div class="team-feature-inner">
    <div class="team-feature-copy">
      <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 24px; display: block;">◆ The Team</span>
      <h2 class="fade-in">A whole team, <em>committed</em><br>to your family.</h2>
      <p class="fade-in">AymanCare isn't built on one physician — it's built on a team. Nurses, medical assistants, and care coordinators who know your face, remember your family, and make every visit feel personal.</p>
      <p class="fade-in">Our staff is bilingual and serves a diverse community — because great care starts with being understood. Across all four clinics, the same people-first standard follows you wherever you go.</p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 32px;" class="fade-in">
        <span class="pill">Board-certified</span>
        <span class="pill pill-accent">Bilingual staff</span>
        <span class="pill pill-outline">English / Spanish / Hindi / Urdu</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-feature-img fade-in">
      <img src="/images/team-photo-v2.jpg" alt="The AymanCare team outside our clinic">
      <div class="team-feature-caption">
        <div class="l">✦ The AymanCare Team</div>
        <div class="t">Care you can count on — from people<br>who know you by name.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="big-cta">
  <div class="big-cta-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in">◆ Easy billing. Easy access.</span>
    <h2 class="fade-in">Here for <em>you</em>,<br>always.</h2>
    <p class="fade-in">AymanCare accepts all major insurance providers. Whether you need immediate treatment or a dedicated healthcare provider for your family long-term, don't hesitate to reach out.</p>
    <div class="cta-row fade-in">
      <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book appointment →</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Contact us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
